QuestData.Title: Vex'tul's Armbands
QuestData.RewardText: Vex'tul has left some of his wrappings within the caravan. Surprisingly, he was courteous enough to keep them folded and separate from everyone else's belongings.$b$bVex'tul values strength over everything else. Leaning in close, you can sense some of his residual strength emanating from within these armbands.
